      "span_text": "In none of Rutishauser's early qd papers (see [CITATION_1] Rutishauser, ,b,c, 1955a ) is there any hint of the LR algorithm yet. (The last of these four papers, on finding eigenvalues with the qd algorithm, was received on July 19, 1954.) What follows is the high point of the drama of the discovery of LR.",
